    <item>
      <title>Taskwarrior Lesson 02: Configuration and Edit Tasks</title>
      <link>http://techtips.billhertzing.com/post/taskwarrior_lesson_02/</link>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Jul 2017 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>http://techtips.billhertzing.com/post/taskwarrior_lesson_02/</guid>
      <description>

&lt;h2 id=&#34;lesson-02:65b895c10bac47a6e8a0dae5d7c8ff68&#34;&gt;Lesson 02&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;iframe width=&#34;560&#34; height=&#34;315&#34; src=&#34;https://www.youtube.com/embed/jutN_S7v13k?ecver=1&#34; frameborder=&#34;0&#34; allowfullscreen&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;

&lt;h3 id=&#34;new-commands:65b895c10bac47a6e8a0dae5d7c8ff68&#34;&gt;New Commands&lt;/h3&gt;

&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code&gt;$ task {task id} edit&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
Line to add to the .bashrc file&lt;br&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code&gt;export EDITOR=&#34;nano&#34;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code&gt;$ task {task id} annotate {additional information}&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
{additional information} This is any text to add to the task.&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
